Mugodhi imhando ye[[hushangazhi]] inochera matombo akakosha kubva muvhu. Matombo aya anogona kunge aine simbi dzakakosha kana kuti achishandiswa mune mamwe mabasa anowanikwa muhushangazhi.


*Munyika yeZimbabwe tine migodhi inochera simbi dzakakosha dzinoti: gold; platiunum; chrome uye lithium. 

*Kunoitawo migodhi inochera mamwe matombo asiri esimbi anoti: diamond; limestone; magnesium uye silicates.


Matombo ane simbi yakakosha anodanwa kunzi [[chitofu]] - (ore kuEnglish).


Matombo asina simbi yakakosha anodanwa kunzi [[mambara]] - (waste rock kuEnglish)
